        void getDocument(java.lang.String dbName,
                 java.lang.String documentId,
                 com.ge.predix.mobile.core.DBTaskCompleteMapCallback mapCallback)
        Returns a document from the database. Note, that if a document with the provided document id does not exist, the success return value in the onComplete closure will still be true, but the returned document dictionary will be nil.
        Parameters:
        dbName - Database name
        documentId - Document Id of document to retrieve
        mapCallback - callback that will be called when the document will be retrieved.

      • updatePullReplicationChannels

        void updatePullReplicationChannels(java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> channelsToAdd,
                                   java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> channelsToRemove,
                                   DBTaskCompleteCallback completeCallback)
        Adds or removes given channel names to pull (server to client) replication
        Parameters:
        channelsToAdd - : String array of channels to add. Pull replication will be restricted to only these channels
        channelsToRemove - : String array of channels to remove. Removing all channels will allow replication of all data to which the user has access.
        completeCallback - : Callback called when assignment of channels is complete. Callback's onComplete will be false if both channelsToAdd and channelsToRemove is nil or an empty array.

      • removeAllChannels

        void removeAllChannels(DBTaskCompleteCallback completeCallback)
        Removes all channel names for pull (server to client) replication
        Parameters:
        completeCallback - : Callback called when assignment of channels is complete.

      • updatePushReplicationFilter

        void updatePushReplicationFilter(java.lang.String filterName,
                                 java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> params,
                                 DBTaskCompleteCallback completeCallback)
        Associates given filter name and filter parameters with push (client to server) replication
        Parameters:
        filterName - : name of filter. This filter must be defined in PredixMobileConfiguration.pushReplicationFilterDefinitions
        params - : Dictionary of filter parameters passed to filter function.
        completeCallback - : Callback called when assignment of filter is complete. Callback's onComplete will be false if filterName is not defined in PredixMobileConfiguration.pushReplicationFilterDefinitions, otherwise true.
